Endpoints:
    POST /sam8/elabora          → esegui pipeline su segnale JSON
    POST /sam8/elabora/batch    → processa N segnali in parallelo
    GET  /sam8/status           → health check + metriche aggregate
    GET  /sam8/docs             → Swagger UI automatico (FastAPI)

Test:
